description: This file declares interface functions and constants for managing Remote Log (RLog) parameters, including get/set/validate/commit/rollback operations, for the Cisco RDK platform.

methods.name: RLog_GetParamBoolValue
methods.description: Retrieves a boolean parameter value for RLog configuration.

methods.name: RLog_GetParamUlongValue
methods.description: Retrieves an unsigned long parameter value for RLog configuration.

methods.name: RLog_GetParamStringValue
methods.description: Retrieves a string parameter value for RLog configuration.

methods.name: RLog_SetParamBoolValue
methods.description: Sets a boolean parameter value for RLog configuration.

methods.name: RLog_SetParamUlongValue
methods.description: Sets an unsigned long parameter value for RLog configuration.

methods.name: RLog_SetParamStringValue
methods.description: Sets a string parameter value for RLog configuration.

methods.name: RLog_Validate
methods.description: Validates RLog parameters before committing changes.

methods.name: RLog_Rollback
methods.description: Rolls back any uncommitted changes to RLog parameters.
